{"tid":10920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"母公司年賺逾4億美元　惠康拒為收銀員提供一張櫈","createTime":"2016-11-29T06:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T11:14:10.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0bf833171ffa3ff02274bd44276248f86128e7ca","tid":10920,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"記者到新界區一間惠康超級市場，以顧客身份與收銀員閒談。有收銀員表示，公司沒有為她們安排椅子，每日由下午3時上班起，要站立至夜晚11時，只有食飯時間才可以到員工休息室坐一會，時限半小時，慨嘆：「搵食係咁㗎喇！腳痛咪用熱水浸吓囉！食得鹹魚抵得渴！」說罷又低頭忙於為顧客收錢。<br />\n<br />\n惠康逾280分店過千收銀「長站」<br />\n<br />\n另一名約40歲收銀苦笑說：「讀唔到書，咪要做呢啲辛苦工囉！」由於店長注視，她不敢再多說。據收銀員表示，惠康收銀員時薪約40元，分店按規模大小，約有6至10多名收銀員不等。據惠康網站資料，全港有逾280間分店，即使按每間分店5名收銀員計算，已有1,400人，若以每店10名收銀計算，人數更多達2,800人。<br />\n<br />\n曾有人向「請給保安員椅子運動」發起人程展緯提到，兩大超市收銀員亦是「無櫈勞工」。因此，他曾到兩大超市約20多間分店巡視，結果發現百佳只有少量超市未有為收銀員提供座椅，而惠康則所有分店都沒有座椅。程展緯於是去信兩大超市，百佳馬上改善，反觀惠康則態度「企硬」，旗下收銀員只能繼續「長站」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/56110/%E6%AF%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%BA%E9%80%BE4%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E6%83%A0%E5%BA%B7%E6%8B%92%E7%82%BA%E6%94%B6%E9%8A%80%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E6%AB%88?utm_content=bufferebe05&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F56110%2F%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E9%2580%25BE4%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583-%25E6%2583%25A0%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%258A%2580%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%25AB%2588%3Futm_content%3Dbufferebe05%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=72f56be1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/56110/%E6%AF%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%BA%E9%80%BE4%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E6%83%A0%E5%BA%B7%E6%8B%92%E7%82%BA%E6%94%B6%E9%8A%80%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E6%AB%88?utm_content=bufferebe05&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a>"},{"pid":"eedd343744b057b2aee2caebefccab949a5f8642","tid":10920,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:18:17.000Z","msg":"「<span style=\"color: red;\">搵食係咁㗎喇！</span>腳痛咪用熱水浸吓囉！食得鹹魚抵得渴！」<br />\n<br />\n好撚憎呢種心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85475f7483268773e27e67fee6536cc0387a6e44","tid":10920,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:19:20.000Z","msg":"冇集體談判權既錯<br />\n邊d人渣做成自已諗"},{"pid":"7ed861dd7c06fdce34978c3ec44f21f127f77021","tid":10920,"uid":20649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"298d45cf7d6765087beddc926c01c085b138f9c7","tid":10920,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"佢地自己都唔爭取<br />\n關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f919c0a48450664492d1ed3a7395ae47e104c9dd","tid":10920,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"廢中連自己人權都唔爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4dd78b45936584dac148548bae95f6b91c862a","tid":10920,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢中連自己人權都唔爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爭取人權=唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n違反獅子山精神"},{"pid":"c7ce60c0fbaf79ce1fd4684727758d6f4a0a3630","tid":10920,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:27: